PAK KIM, PENYELUNDUP ORANG

554
00:41:37,594 --> 00:41:39,054
Hei, Pak Kim!

555
00:41:39,137 --> 00:41:40,430
Ini aku, Seok Jeong-ho.

556
00:41:40,514 --> 00:41:41,515
Ya.

557
00:41:41,807 --> 00:41:43,183
Apa kabar?

558
