Sebaiknya, kau menepati janji itu.

577
00:43:39,799 --> 00:43:40,800
Mengerti?

578
00:43:51,853 --> 00:43:56,608
SEONHWAGAK

579
00:44:03,657 --> 00:44:05,242
Aku ditelepon makelar penyelundup.

580
00:44:05,325 --> 00:44:07,410
Dia bermarkas di Incheon.
