585
00:44:14,834 --> 00:44:15,961
Aku akan pergi sekarang.

586
00:44:16,711 --> 00:44:17,712
Baiklah.

587
00:44:41,194 --> 00:44:42,737
WANMYEONG-DAERO, SEO-GU

588
00:45:01,381 --> 00:45:02,382
Hai!

589
00:45:02,465 --> 00:45:03,675
Selamat datang, Pak.

590
00:45:09,264 --> 00:45:10,307
Kapan kapalnya berangkat?

591
00:45:12,058 --> 00:45:13,893
Dua sampai tiga jam lagi.

592
00:45:23,278 --> 00:45:25,030
Aku akan membayar sisanya
begitu aku tiba.

593
